From: Oleksandr Natalenko <oleksandr@natalenko.name>
Subject: [pf-curated-6.12] pksm: process_ksm_{enable,disable,status} + KSM mm hooks

Re-cut from natalenko's pf-kernel branch pksm-6.12 (tip c9ed6345b0ea)
as a single bulk diff, restricted to the files this overlay's curation
kept on the 6.12 LTS slot. Source: codeberg.org/pf-kernel/linux.

Branch renamed from ksm-6.X to pksm-6.12 ('process KSM') but the
syscall set is the same as 6.6's three-syscall scheme — process_ksm_*
at 453-455 across all architectures.
